stories.text:
Hi! I wanted to share with you what we created.

We have been working on BOWWE for over 7 years, perfecting it to be the best no-code and low-code platform. BOWWE is a great tool for anyone who wants to create a website, without having to learn how to code. With BOWWE, you can create functional websites, with ease, using our drag-and-drop system, customizable templates, and widgets. Moreover, we also allow building landing and micro pages, portfolios and CVs. BOWWE has high-quality code and top-notch SEO, which will increase the website's ranking in search engines.

Some of the cool features we have: • Predefined and custom integrations- create your own integrations with any API/tool or use ones we prepared. • Beautiful and extensive UI Kit • RAW templates, blocks, sections, and templates • Pixel Perfect- create and adjust your designs with pixel-perfect precision.

We know that not everything works perfectly in BOWWE there are still places that can be improved, features that can be added, so any suggestions and thoughts are welcome!
